North Pacific from the Bering Sea to Japan ( Antsulevich 2015 ); possibly from Alaska to Oregon ( Fraser 1937 ). Records of the species from the North Pacific by Nutting (1901b) , Stechow (1913) and Fraser (1937) were considered questionable by Schuchert (2008b) .
